The LANGE 1 TOURBILLON “25th Anniversary”

   Discover the LANGE 1 TOURBILLON “25th Anniversary”
   Explore timepiece

Our 2019 debuts

   At the Geneva Salon (SIHH) we have presented our latest debuts to the
   public.
   Explore timepieces

ZEITWERK DATE

   Ingeniously integrated in an award-winning concept: the ZEITWERK DATE
   is A. Lange & Söhne’s first mechanical digital watch with a date
   function.
   Explore timepiece

1815 ANNUAL CALENDAR

   The second Lange timepiece with the eponymous function follows the
   classic construction and design principles of the 1815 watch family.
   EXPLORE TIMEPIECES
   The LANGE 1 in pink gold (191.032), seen here from the side, is one of
   many timepieces from A. Lange & Söhne.

   EXPLORE NOW

Discover our Timepieces

   EXPLORE NOW

„The entire pursuit of a watchmaker should be the perfection of each and
every watch.”

   Signature of Ferdinand Adolph Lange on a white background Learn more
   about A. Lange & Söhne
   Wilhelm Schmid, CEO of A. Lange & Söhne, being interviewed at SIHH
   2018.

